<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Вход — CRM FitnessClub</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { background: #14161a; color: #f5f5f5; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .card-login { background: #1c1f26; border: 1px solid #262b34; max-width: 400px; width: 100%; color: #f5f5f5; }
        .card-login h1 { color: #f5f5f5; }
        .legal-note { font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.45; color: #a8adb8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .legal-note a { color: #ffcb45; text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card card-login rounded-3 p-4 shadow">
    <h1 class="h5 mb-3">Вход в CRM</h1>
    {% if error %}
        <div class="alert alert-danger py-2 small">{{ error.messageKey|trans(error.messageData, 'security') }}</div>
    {% endif %}
    <form method="post" action="{{ path('admin_login_check') }}">
        <label class="form-label small text-secondary">Email</label>
        <input type="email" class="form-control form-control-sm mb-2" name="_username" value="{{ last_username }}" required autofocus autocomplete="username">
        <label class="form-label small text-secondary">Пароль</label>
        <input type="password" class="form-control form-control-sm mb-3" name="_password" required autocomplete="current-password">
        <input type="hidden" name="_csrf_token" value="{{ csrf_token('authenticate') }}">
        <p class="legal-note">
            Нажимая кнопку «Войти» Вы подтверждаете, что ознакомлены с
            <a href="{{ path('legal_privacy') }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Политикой конфиденциальности</a>
            и принимаете условия
            <a href="{{ path('legal_license_agreement') }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Договора</a>.
        </p>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning w-100">Войти</button>
    </form>
</div>
</body>
</html>
